---

<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<ThemeLayout>
  <Layout>
    <section class="min-h-screen bg-black/40 p-6 rounded-md text-white px-6 py-2 flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="flex w-full max-w-5xl gap-12">
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-12">
            <h3 class="border-l-4 border-blue-500/50 p-5 text-m text-blue-300/40">
            the existence of syncheion city is proof that the gods are still with us.
            </h3>
         </div>

        <section class="col-span-full">
          <br>
          <blockquote class="inline text-pink-100/30"> ...that's what they say, anyway. </blockquote>
          <br>
          <blockquote class="inline text-pink-300/50"> I'll let you decide for yourself.</blockquote>
          <code class="inline text-pink-300/50">-I</code>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="block p-6 px-20">
        <br>
        <p>
          Syncheion is a sprawling metropolis in the middle of a wasteland world. With an eclectic mix of cultures
          and an edge for technological innovation, it's fast approaching the top of the list for "cities that could
          become the next Tower of Babylon".
        </p>
        <p>
          That's right - the wrath of the gods is stewing, and it's only a matter of time before the
          floodgates break.
        </p>
        <p>
          Again.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="min-h-screen bg-black/40 p-4 rounded-md text-white px-10 py-1 flex flex-col items-center">
      <p class="text-cyan-100/50"> waiting for that all-important entry permit? check out some stories in the meantime. </p>
      <ProseList posts={prosePosts} />
    </section>

  </Layout>
</ThemeLayout>